// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2269 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: a052bb2a-1611-5d01-8158-6be2f71656e9

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
